2015-01-14  Bo-cheng Jan <school510587@yahoo.com.tw>

	* src/tools/init_database.c: init_database.c: Resolve queue-full
	exception The circular queue is full with head = tail, which is
	indistinguishable from empty case. So we set q_len to one more than
	the maximum number of elements it actually needs.  Signed-off-by: Jim Huang <jserv@0xlab.org>

