2013-10-04  ChangZhuo Chen (é™³æ˜Œå€¬) <czchen@gmail.com>

	* src/hash.c: Do not read negative frequency A negative frequency might occur due to #75. To avoid these bogus
	phrase, libchewing shall not read any phrase that has negative
	frequency.

