	* : commit c54c0992430c0d944c88e224ddeebfcb01844adf Merge: 2a9279f
	0d8bd5e Author: ChangZhuo Chen (é™³æ˜Œå€¬) <czchen@gmail.com> Date:
	Tue Sep 24 04:42:28 2013 -0700

2013-09-24  ChangZhuo Chen (é™³æ˜Œå€¬) <czchen@gmail.com>

	* include/internal/memory-private.h, src/hash.c: Use properly
	getter/setter to access binary data In current libchewing, system dictionary is platform independent,
	while user dictionary is platform dependent (more precisely, endian
	dependent). In order to address this different, the suffix
	PreservedEndian is added when this getter/setter is platform
	dependent.

2013-09-23  ChangZhuo Chen (é™³æ˜Œå€¬) <czchen@gmail.com>

	* src/choice.c: Fix cannot select candidate when symbol exists Closed #84

