	* test/test-bopomofo.c, test/test-regression.c: Add test cases for
	candidate selecting with symbol These test cases are designed for candidate selecting while there is
	a symbol in preedit buffer (See #79 and #84). The original
	regression test case for #79 is removed because it is covered by
	these cases.

