	* src/chewingio.c, test/test-bopomofo.c, test/testhelper.h: Space
	can change to shorter candidate list When using space as selection key, it shall change to shorter
	candidate list when it is in the last page of current candidate
	list. In this way, user can use just space to replace down and
	right.  Closed #82

