2013-09-20  ChangZhuo Chen (é™³æ˜Œå€¬) <czchen@gmail.com>

	* src/chewingutil.c: Do not add userphrase whe auto commit We does not know if the whole auto commit string is a valid phrase.
	It might contain symbol. Also, it causes memory leak due to mismatch
	phoneSeq and wordSeq.  Closed #80

2013-09-20  ChangZhuo Chen (é™³æ˜Œå€¬) <czchen@gmail.com>

	* src/hash.c: Do not use recursive call to free hash item

2013-09-19  ChangZhuo Chen (é™³æ˜Œå€¬) <czchen@gmail.com>

	* src/choice.c, test/test-regression.c: Fix cannot select candidate
	when symbol exists pgdata->phoneSeq skips all symbols in preedit buffer, while
	pgdata->bSymbolArrBrkpt does not skip any symbols. They have
	different index system (skip symbol vs. not skip symbol) so we
	cannot use them together. To use pgdata->bSymbolArrBrkpt and
	pgdata->phoneSeq together, translation is needed in one of them.  Closed #79

