2013-08-30  ChangZhuo Chen (é™³æ˜Œå€¬) <czchen@gmail.com>

	* CMakeLists.txt: Fix several cmake build problems The following issues are fixed: *   `make clean' in in tree build
	    does not remove pinyin.tab, swkb.dat, symbols.dat now.  *   phoneid.dic is removed during build process.  *   `make install'
	now installs pinyin.tab, swkb.dat, symbols.dat.  Closed #67

