	* src/private.h: Rewrite macro STATIC_ASSERT to avoid recent GCC
	warnings Reference:   http://www.pixelbeat.org/programming/gcc/static_assert.html

2013-05-17  ChangZhuo Chen <czchen@gmail.com>

